pulltitle: Add tooltips, add footer links, assorted cleanup
pullsbody:
- Added tooltips to markers on the map
- Footer images now link to the appropriate sites
- Cleaned up page templates
- The map no longer wraps (you won't see repeating continents if you zoom out)
- The footer now sticks to the bottom of the page
